{"tid":1975080,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"LIHKG 箍牙集中討論佢23","createTime":"2020-04-16T09:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:02:43.000Z","uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"299d57c25b0743f703a6762fde74b6ff47c04374","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"個個post都有人問邊個牙醫好<br />\n其實大家可以去下面個list慢慢揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙齒矯正科專科醫生名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dchk.org.hk/docs/SA_Orthodontics.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dchk.org.hk%2Fdocs%2FSA_Orthodontics.pdf&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10EXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e9ef2e99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dchk.org.hk/docs/SA_Orthodontics.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n開始箍牙之後大概一個月覆診一次<br />\n所以揀個近屋企嘅會比較方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果排牙唔係好亂/budget有限<br />\n搵普通科牙醫都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通科牙醫名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dchk.org.hk/docs/List_of_Registered_Dentists_Local.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dchk.org.hk%2Fdocs%2FList_of_Registered_Dentists_Local.pdf&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10EXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=ea40517a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dchk.org.hk/docs/List_of_Registered_Dentists_Local.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n傳統鋼箍會比隱適美有力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問排牙複雜既都係用鋼箍好<br />\n建議各位巴絲打係決定揀邊個牙醫前<br />\n先諮詢2-3個牙醫意見先再作決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個牙醫做法都唔同，可以各自比對下療程方式及價錢/服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350afdcd5ffe0f71fba273d9a69deaf14fbe4613","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"估唔到我中左1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79807c980e41ae42599ce5e6c509cc091f9c759a","tid":1975080,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350afdcd5ffe0f71fba273d9a69deaf14fbe4613","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"估唔到我中左1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T09:46:22.000Z","msg":"謝謝開帖"},{"pid":"db750466a263d5e39ec8cc4a3a924ade16791cf6","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"我想問下少少問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我2月尾開始上箍，到今個星期剝左一邊2隻牙，下星期再剝另一邊<br />\n1. 有冇巴絲掮左2-3個月，食比較硬既野(例如 : 牛柳) D牙都會麻麻地及痛痛地? <br />\n<br />\n2. 醫生講話剝曬牙之後，先開始排番個位置，最後要箍番齊。黎個時間係點嫁....我擔心食野仲係食唔到硬野"},{"pid":"4fe7d18607fff5a97ba486c9bb0adf38762336cb","tid":1975080,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db750466a263d5e39ec8cc4a3a924ade16791cf6","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"我想問下少少問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我2月尾開始上箍，到今個星期剝左一邊2隻牙，下星期再剝另一邊<br />\n1. 有冇巴絲掮左2-3個月，食比較硬既野(例如 : 牛柳) D牙都會麻麻地及痛痛地? <br />\n<br />\n2. 醫生講話剝曬牙之後，先開始排番個位置，最後要箍番齊。黎個時間係點嫁....我擔心食野仲係食唔到硬野"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"1. 你食得多唔多 定係只係咬一下就痛<br />\n2. 要睇你啲牙本身亂唔亂 我箍半年 牙本身唔亂 都仲排緊位<br />\n<br />\n同埋好似開左另一個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85570cc2a4a9dbfe22928f99d47ff9110c8ad2ef","tid":1975080,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe7d18607fff5a97ba486c9bb0adf38762336cb","tid":1975080,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db750466a263d5e39ec8cc4a3a924ade16791cf6","tid":1975080,"uid":252477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"我想問下少少問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/